law.history: Repealed 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 258, sec. 5, effective July 15, 1996. -- Repealed and reenacted as a new section of KRS ch. 39 by 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 188, sec. 142, effective July 15, 1980. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 155, sec. 116, effective June 17, 1978. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 74, Art. IV, sec. 20(5) and (6). -- Amended 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 179, sec. 79, effective March 25, 1960. -- Created 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 57, sec. 4.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Restrictions on use of appropriated funds.
